query:
DELETE FROM timeEntries 
WHERE assignmentId IN (
  SELECT epa.id FROM employeeProjectAssignments epa
  JOIN employees e ON epa.employeeId = e.id
  WHERE e.firstName = 'Maciej' AND e.lastName = 'K'
) 
AND YEAR(workDate) = 2025 AND MONTH(workDate) = 12
